+# Task Queue System Design
+
+## Architecture
+
+Single `TaskQueue` class exported from `src/index.ts` managing all state.
+
+## Core Data Model
+
+```ts
+type TaskStatus = 'pending' | 'processing' | 'completed' | 'failed' | 'cancelled' | 'blocked';
+
+interface Task<P = unknown> {
+  id: string;                    // UUID v4
+  queueName: string;
+  payload: P;
+  status: TaskStatus;
+  priority: number;              // 1-10, default 5
+  createdAt: Date;
+  availableAt: Date;             // for delayed tasks
+  attempts: number;              // retry count
+  maxRetries: number;            // default 3
+  baseDelay: number;             // backoff base ms, default 1000
+  dependsOn: string[];           // task IDs
+  progress: number;              // 0-100
+  progressMessage?: string;
+  error?: Error;
+  lastFailedAt?: Date;
+}
+```
+
+## Internal Queue State (per named queue)
+
+- `pending: Task[]` — sorted by (priority ASC, availableAt ASC, createdAt ASC)
+- `processing: Set<string>` — task IDs currently processing
+- `dlq: Task[]` — dead letter queue
+- `maxConcurrency: number | null`
+- `middleware: MiddlewareFn[]`
+- `handler?: HandlerFn`
+- `schedules: Map<string, Schedule>`
+
+## Key Algorithms
+
+### dequeue(queueName)
+1. Check concurrency limit; return null if at cap
+2. Filter pending tasks where `availableAt <= now` AND `status !== blocked`
+3. Sort: priority ASC, availableAt ASC, createdAt ASC
+4. Return first; mark processing
+
+### complete(taskId)
+1. Mark completed
+2. Release concurrency slot
+3. Check if any blocked tasks now unblocked (all deps completed)
+4. Unblock them → pending
+
+### fail(taskId, error)
+1. Increment attempts
+2. If attempts < maxRetries: compute backoff delay, re-queue as pending with new availableAt
+3. Else: move to DLQ
+
+### Dependency detection (phase 7)
+- On add: validate all dep IDs exist
+- Detect cycles: DFS from new task following dependsOn edges; if new task reachable, cycle exists
+
+## Middleware (phase 11)
+```ts
+type MiddlewareFn = (task: Task, next: () => Promise<void>) => Promise<void>;
+```
+Composed like Koa middleware.
+
+## Shutdown (phase 12)
+- `shuttingDown` flag blocks new task adds
+- Wait for `processing` sets to drain across all queues
+- Force-cancel after timeout
+
+## File Structure
+```
+src/
+  index.ts          — public API exports
+  TaskQueue.ts      — main class
+  types.ts          — all shared types
+  utils.ts          — UUID, sorting helpers
+  cron.ts           — cron expression parser/evaluator
+```
